# Amazon Price Searcher

Amazon Price Searcher is a web app that allows users to search for items on Amazon.com and compare their prices across different Amazon websites (Amazon.com, Amazon.co.uk, Amazon.de, and Amazon.ca). The app also keeps a history of past searches.

## Features

- Search for items on Amazon.com
- Compare item prices across Amazon.com, Amazon.co.uk, Amazon.de, and Amazon.ca
- Display item prices in USD
- Save search history in a local SQLite database
- (Optional) Implement user authentication using Google Sign-In
- (Optional) Link search history to specific users
- (Optional) Implement a daily search limit per user

## Technologies Used

- Backend: Flask (Python)
- Frontend: HTML, JavaScript
- Web Scraping: Beautiful Soup, Requests
- Database: SQLite

